{
  "stem": "26142.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my sister-in-law and the children slept in that bed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the three brothers, the three of us, slept on the floor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember we were-- we were laying on the floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my brother, Moshe-- --he was-- he was the-- the pious, the religious one in our family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and maybe the-- the-- the weight of the responsibility that he had there-- his two little children and his wife-- he-- I remember, took out a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He didn't go to sleep till 12.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He took out a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he asked us, he asked my brother-- Tsvi and I-- he says, what day of [NON-ENGLISH] is there?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew it's before Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What day of [NON-ENGLISH] is it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we figured it out somehow that this is the fourth day of [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That is said before Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's why I knew it was before Rosh Hashanah, because we didn't say [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember-- I remember watching him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember seeing-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] tears coming down his eyes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [CRYING] Anyway, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] exactly 12 o'clock, we said goodbye to the people of-- we didn't want to wake them up.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We said goodbye by then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- they did come out and-- to say goodbye to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the man came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we took-- and we were afraid that we will wake the children up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the children will start crying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Up to this day, I wonder what kind of miracles that the children didn't-- didn't-- they-- they-- they-- there's some kind of a mysterious force in them that kept them-- that they knew what-- what the situation is.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I remember I was carrying the little [NON-ENGLISH] in my hand.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
